ory><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><description>Learn when to skip intermediate grits and use a sandpaper grit chart for faster, flawless finishes on wood, paint, and metal.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="when-you-can-skip-grits-a-sandpaper-grit-chart-guide"&gt;When You Can Skip Grits: A Sandpaper Grit Chart Guide&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ve cleared a corner of the garage, moved the bikes just enough to set out sawhorses, and wrestled a wobbly dresser onto the stands. It’s late, your playlist is humming, and there’s a small mountain of sanding discs beside you—80, 100, 120, 150, 180, 220, 320. You glance at the packaging diagram, then pull up a sandpaper grit chart on your phone, wondering if you really have to touch every single step. You’re not restoring a museum piece; you just want this dresser to look clean and feel smooth before paint. How many passes will it take? How many hours?&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/18.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/15/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/when-you-can-skip-intermediate-grits-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Task Matching By Grit Range</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 06 Nov 2025 16:30:50 +0000</pubDate><category>Grit Range &amp; Classification</category><category>grit-40</category><category>grit-60</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-100</category><category>grit-101</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-240</category><description>Learn how to match tasks to sandpaper grit for wood, metal, and paint. Clear ranges, tool pairings, and pro tips for smooth, consistent results.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="task-matching-by-sandpaper-grit-a-practical-guide"&gt;Task Matching by Sandpaper Grit: A Practical Guide&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The project usually begins with confidence: a sunny Saturday, a coffee within reach, and a table or bike part you’re finally ready to refresh. You pull out the sander, grab whatever sandpaper is on top, and get to work. Ten minutes later, the surface looks worse—deep scratches in one spot, shiny untouched coatings in another, and dust everywhere. It’s a moment most DIYers and even pros have felt: the work is happening, but progress isn’t. The missing piece is rarely effort. It’s almost always selection—specifically, matching the task to the right sandpaper grit.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/pinterest/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/pinterest/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/pinterest/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/task-matching-by-grit-range-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>10</readingTime></item><item><title>How To Choose A Starting Grit</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 06 Nov 2025 15:25:52 +0000</pubDate><category>Grit Guide &amp; Education</category><category>grit chart</category><category>abrasive standards</category><category>grit progression</category><category>grit-60</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-101</category><category>grit-120</category><category>clear coat</category><category>orbital sander</category><description>Learn how to choose your starting grit with a clear sandpaper grit chart, shop-tested sequences, and pro tips for clean, fast, and flat sanding.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="sandpaper-grit-chart-choose-the-right-starting-grit"&gt;Sandpaper Grit Chart: Choose the Right Starting Grit&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first time I watched a flawless finish come alive, it happened in the last ten minutes of a long Saturday in the shop. Cold radio in the background, dust collector humming, I wiped a splash of mineral spirits across a dining tabletop and the grain popped like a film reveal. That moment didn’t come from luck—it came from choosing the right starting grit. I keep a small sandpaper grit chart taped to my cabinet door, not because I can’t memorize grits, but because the surface in front of you changes the rules. A hundred-year-old oak stained dark is not the same as new maple fresh off the planer. Paint sprayed last month is not like six coats of hand-brushed oil from the 90s. The trick is reading the job, then picking the grit that does the heavy lifting without making more work.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/instagram/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/pinterest/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/06/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart/cards/facebook/how-to-choose-a-starting-grit-sandpaper-grit-chart.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Coarse Medium Fine And Ultra Fine Definitions</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 03 Nov 2025 05:39:06 +0000</pubDate><category>Grit Range &amp; Classification</category><category>grit-101</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-180</category><category>clear coat</category><category>sanding block</category><category>wet sanding</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Understand coarse, medium, fine, and ultra fine sandpaper grit with practical steps, pro tips, and troubleshooting for flawless surfaces.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="coarse-to-ultra-fine-sandpaper-grit-decoded"&gt;Coarse to Ultra Fine: Sandpaper Grit Decoded&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Saturday morning in the shop. Coffee on the bench, a drop cloth draped over a dented heirloom dresser you promised to rescue. You pull open the top drawer and the musty smell of old lacquer and stubborn pine dust hits the air. A sanding block lies beside a stack of sheets you picked up at the hardware store—some marked 60, others 120, 220, even 400. You know each number stands for a sandpaper grit, but right now they feel like a foreign language. The last time you “winged it,” you left swirl marks that telegraphed straight through your stain, and spent another weekend fixing what you rushed the first time.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/facebook/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit/cards/instagram/coarse-medium-fine-and-ultra-fine-definitions-sandpaper-grit.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/03/c